		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />x=256-320 is still plenty of window. Only the last two writes absolutely have to be within the window, and there are 5 cycles (15-16 dots) from the beginning of one write to the end of the second, that still leaves 48 dots, or 15-16 cycles.

		

